body:
@rovere pointed out that maximum number that can be stored to 4 bits is 15, and therefore a `static_assert` in `SiPixelClusterShapeCache::insert()` has a bug. In practice, the largest array that has been inserted has a capacity of 9, so the bug should have had no effect. But better to fix anyway.

Tested in 9_0_0_pre4, no changes expected.

@rovere @VinInn
